📌 Project Overview
This project implements the K-Nearest Neighbors (K-NN) algorithm to predict whether a customer will purchase a car based on their age and estimated salary.

📂 Dataset
File: car_purchase_data.csv
Columns:
Age (Independent variable)
Estimated Salary (Independent variable)
Purchased (Dependent variable: 0 = No, 1 = Yes)
🛠️ Libraries Used
numpy
pandas
matplotlib
sklearn (for model training and evaluation)
